text: The 2019 Carling Black Label Cup was the eighth edition of the Carling Black Label Cup to be held. ==Venue== The FNB Stadium was chosen to host this annual event. The FNB Stadium, known as Soccer City during the 2010 FIFA World Cup, is a stadium located in Nasrec, the Soweto area of Johannesburg, South Africa. ==Match== ===Details=== ==Notes== Category:Soccer cup competitions in South Africa Carling
title: 2019 Carling Black Label Cup
